title: He's A 10 But... ft. MissRemiAshten & Oli Abbas
description:
Lauren is joined by Remi & Oli to play an iconic round of "He's a 10 But..." They reminisce on Remi's encounter with a scammy psychic and Oli brings a surprise to the WT9 set. 

Right now, when you go to heyfavor.com/WILD, Favor is offering a $10 donation to Bedsider.org for every Wild Til 9 listener who becomes a patient. Your donation will help low-income individuals get access to birth control through Bedsider.org.
